{"id": "1507269426033201242", "channel_id": "1507269426033201242", "author_id": "808924960491569263", "author_name": "jhhh_mkk", "content": "主線打得越來越辛苦，星辰篇3-6甚至沒拿滿星😭，有些關卡需甚至要用復活才能過，想提升隊伍強度，拜託各位老師了😭🙏", "timestamp": "2026-05-22T06:30:34.878000+00:00", "thread_id": "1507269426033201242", "attachments": [{"id": "1507269426280530131", "filename": "Screenshot_20260522_140949.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 194149, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1507269426033201242/1507269426280530131/Screenshot_20260522_140949.jpg?ex=6a11f24a&is=6a10a0ca&hm=29928d9a937883760ae24849f084da4f80b072ef7114122937bb17e1bfa68ace&"}, {"id": "1507269426754355281", "filename": "Screenshot_20260522_141007.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 192395, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1507269426033201242/1507269426754355281/Screenshot_20260522_141007.jpg?ex=6a11f24b&is=6a10a0cb&hm=e353d3a83db40dfbab2e00186e7a07b56dc695a5a3921473f8f46c1b5f6494df&"}, {"id": "1507269427157139526", "filename": "Screenshot_20260522_141023.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 191336, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1507269426033201242/1507269427157139526/Screenshot_20260522_141023.jpg?ex=6a11f24b&is=6a10a0cb&hm=27701ac6dff91f8d3f97db05099d2584a5a939837f62e75ae2c83b1b843652bf&"}, {"id": "1507269427551273080", "filename": "Screenshot_20260522_141314.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 160499, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1507269426033201242/1507269427551273080/Screenshot_20260522_141314.jpg?ex=6a11f24b&is=6a10a0cb&hm=ea86c5f87da3bc315e25aafcd0b12396374a18cf20735458e9bc8acb06adcfd3&"}, {"id": "1507269428059050006", "filename": "Screenshot_20260522_142843.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 80602, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1507269426033201242/1507269428059050006/Screenshot_20260522_142843.jpg?ex=6a11f24b&is=6a10a0cb&hm=b257124ebb3673ace7dbca195ebdcac0ec6c3ca9b81789cee265ed0d266138a1&"}]}
